sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant FE as Frontend (React)
  participant API as Backend (FastAPI)
  participant DB as Database

  U->>FE: Submit email + password
  FE->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/login
  API->>API: slowapi rate-limit check (10/min)
  API->>DB: SELECT users WHERE email=?
  DB-->>API: user row
  API->>API: bcrypt.verify(password, user.hashed_password)
  alt Valid
    API->>API: Build JWT access (30 min) + refresh (7 d)
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_logs(action='login.success')
    API-->>FE: 200 { access_token, refresh_token, user }
    FE->>FE: Persist tokens (Zustand + localStorage)
    FE->>U: Redirect by role to dashboard
  else Invalid
    API->>DB: INSERT audit_logs(action='login.failed')
    API-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
    FE->>U: Show error toast
  end

  Note over FE,API: All subsequent calls send Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
  Note over FE: Axios interceptor catches 401 → refresh once → else clear auth + /login
